### Icon List (Widget)

Used for a bulleted list with custom icons.

  * `elType`: `"widget"`
  * `widgetType`: `"icon-list"`
  * `elements`: Must be `[]`.
  * `settings`:
      * `icon_list`: An array of objects. Each object has `text` (the list item) and optionally `selected_icon` (an icon object with `value` and `library`).

**Example (Icon List):**

```json
{
  "id": "2bee7be7",
  "elType": "widget",
  "isInner": false,
  "widgetType": "icon-list",
  "settings": {
    "icon_list": [
      {
        "text": "Feature One",
        "_id": "b406229",
        "selected_icon": { "value": "fas fa-check", "library": "fa-solid" }
      },
      {
        "text": "Feature Two",
        "_id": "2429975",
        "selected_icon": { "value": "fas fa-check", "library": "fa-solid" }
      }
    ],
    "icon_size": { "unit": "px", "size": 20, "sizes": [] },
    "text_color": "#333333"
  },
  "elements": []
}
```

